review_data.title: Great place!
review_data.content: The food was very tasty, the owner super nice, there's a shop of African food ingredients, an eatery and a gallery. Heartily recommended.

review_data.title: Delicious african food in Zürich
review_data.content: This restaurant/take away was a real discovery. The food is really good and the owner reall friendly. I took the beef in peanut sauce with two types of rice and vegetables and everything was just delicious.
